<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>187</hymn_number>
<title>NA SUNPARNAK AN CHIM CH187</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nangmah sunparnak kha an chim, Zion, kan Pathian khuapi Zungzal a
 hmunmi Pathian nih, A umnak ca-ah an ser; Zungzal Lungpi cung sakmi cu,
 Zei nih dah an hninh khawh lai? Khamhnak hau in kulh na si i, Na ral kha
 na tih hna lo.

[V2]
 Zohhmanh, zungzal dawtnak chungin, Nunnak ti cu a rung luang, Na fale
 vialte a cawm hna, Chamhbaunak an tih lai lo, Cu bantuk tiva luan lio ah,
 Hodah tihal in ba lai? Bawipa a kan petu thawngin, Velngeihnak a dong lai
 lo.

[V3]
 A hmunkip velchum hna ah cun, Lianhngannak, himnak ca ah, Mei le
 khuadawm cu an lo i, Bawipa a nai hngalhnak ca, Zungzal Lungpi cung sakmi
 cu, Zei nih dah an hninh khawh lai? Khamhnak hau in kulh na si i, Na ral
 kha na tih hna lo.</lyrics>
</song>